OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,FThe Lebanese Ministry of Health says
OL,7,F131 healthcare workers have been
OL,8,Fkilled since this war between Israel
OL,9,Fand Hezbollah resumed on March 2 this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FLast week, civil defence workers
OL,13,Fstruggled to extinguish a fire at the
OL,14,Fcity's main hospital after it was
OL,15,Fshattered by an Israeli airstrike.
OL,17,FAt the centre of those efforts was 18-
OL,18,Fyear-old Hussein Safedine, a student
OL,19,Fwho volunteers to do one of the most
OL,20,Fperilous jobs on earth. He told me he
OL,21,Fis not scared.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
