OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,FThey showed us footage shot on their
OL,7,Fbody cam as they pulled a wounded
OL,8,Fcolleague from a burning emergency
OL,9,Fvehicle, like so many of those
OL,10,Fdestroyed here had been clearly marked
OL,11,Fwith a red cross and a red crescent.
OL,13,FThe team told us they now wait five
OL,14,Fminutes before entering the location
OL,15,Fof an Israeli airstrike, for fear of a
OL,16,Fsecond, a so-called "double tap"
OL,17,Fstrike, which has already claimed the
OL,18,Flives of many of their colleagues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
