OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,FWhen tactics like these were used
OL,7,Fagainst the White Helmets during
OL,8,FSyria's civil war, there was worldwide
OL,9,Fcondemnation.
OL,11,FThe men we spoke to in Tyre are still
OL,12,Fwaiting for the same reaction here.
OL,14,FAli Safedine, the leader of this
OL,15,Fdivision, told us of his daily fears:
OL,16,F"Every moment, every second, we expect
OL,17,Fto lose someone from my team, even me;
OL,18,FI expect to die.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
