OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,F"Every day when our team goes towards,
OL,7,FI strike, I worry one of us will never
OL,8,Fcome back.
OL,10,F"But we will carry on, even if only
OL,11,Fone of us is still alive; he will
OL,12,Fdrive our ambulance to the wounded."
OL,14,FOn the back of their ambulance, they
OL,15,Fcarry an image of Paramedic Hadi Daher.
OL,17,FJust six weeks ago, ITV News was
OL,18,Ftalking to Hadi and his colleagues in
OL,19,FTyre. He died in an airstrike while
OL,20,Fanswering an emergency call just two
OL,21,Fweeks later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
