OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,FBack at Tyre's main hospital, Jabal
OL,7,FAmel, we went to see the damage from a
OL,8,Fstrike that had taken out buildings
OL,9,Fnearby and severely damaged the
OL,10,Fhospital itself.
OL,12,FThe medical director showed us holes
OL,13,Fpunched through walls, which wounded
OL,14,Ffour doctors and 32 other staff
OL,15,Fmembers.
OL,17,FDr Wael Mroueh, the hospital boss,
OL,18,Fcompared the situation in Lebanon to
OL,19,Fthat of Palestine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
