OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"You know what happened in Gaza, so
OL,12,Fyou know they are repeating this
OL,13,Fhere," he said.
OL,15,F"They say a lot, but you journalists
OL,16,Fhave seen the bombed-out places.
OL,17,FThey're just trying to get us to
OL,18,Fleave."
OL,20,FInside, the main cardiac care centre
OL,21,Fis completely wrecked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
