OL,3,CHow Lebanon's volunteer medics risk
OL,4,Ctheir lives amid Israeli strikes
OL,6,FThe Geneva Conventions demand that
OL,7,Fhospitals not be attacked, but also
OL,8,Fthat they be respected and protected.
OL,10,FThe people of Tyre may have reason to
OL,11,Fwonder whether international law still
OL,12,Fapplies in their city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
